{"h5a00ba48gb00dg42ecga528g1532d90c6730": ["Stop! I give up! M-mercy, please!", "b2c582af-bc69-48b3-a004-648562dab404", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "9ce1b6b8-e2c6-1f68-51ab-ca3a89ce2755"], "h4f84f154g00dcg4c7cgad7fg137d1675e856": ["I know things, if you l-let me live, I'll make it worth your while. I p-promise!", "b2c582af-bc69-48b3-a004-648562dab404", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "98648383-9a14-4dea-97c1-d2bb60c8c48c"], "hd3f28858g8c88g4dd0g9bcdge2ef9b1cdb99": ["Let me do the talking.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "b85c6a83-ca02-a374-f072-cace737cc351"], "hdfecc5cbgcaedg4a5dg9c7eg035fbdc51f0f": ["Go ahead. Ask your questions, Wyll.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "4a628784-7072-acd4-1a80-a545e666230a"], "h94e47cc6g93d0g496bg8d22ge9cd68a95105": ["Mizora - the prisoner at your camp. <i>Where did the drow take her?</i>", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "d66356e5-7696-b950-71f0-f4ceada7f850"], "h808f1430g5702g4fcega42dg6617df2ce168": ["The lady Spike nabbed? Drow hauled 'er to Moonrise - jus' over the mountain pass!", "b2c582af-bc69-48b3-a004-648562dab404", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "b14a651d-c53a-390f-236a-dcf67b29dc1c"], "hc4fda08bga8bcg4152g99bag443603332dee": ["Perfect. That's what I needed.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "86b4abc5-0258-35d3-8f47-3178f2c94d0f"], "h2e4eca5eg89b4g4d3egb288g00fa4e0574f3": ["<i>Kill it.</i>", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "ebf0db33-a013-76f9-3a4a-321d803657ff"], "h62b0bb41gcfffg4c35g94e4gebe471020525": ["<i>Deliver the final blow.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "9afe6c47-972c-3e31-134b-548697d2f0f4"], "h9539b3f7g5218g4c93g9d66g521163b77922": ["N-n-noo!", "b2c582af-bc69-48b3-a004-648562dab404", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "66b4430c-a79a-f1a9-99d1-7df941ac4d73"], "h912ae8afg727dg476bgbe76g498a4ad54c7e": ["Forget it - if you want him dead, kill him yourself.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "6e699a22-9332-dd3b-10dc-3a3bc7f638c4"], "h5623a616g203bg4a84gab38gfde8806d4690": ["With pleasure.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "9a746292-7c9c-c82e-f358-1707aa4e8392"], "hb090e197gd74eg48ecg995ag16532eb8f33c": ["I'm in a merciful mood. Run, goblin.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "e3af33a3-d64d-ad0b-2e76-ac48bf0eaac1"], "he6747fbcg56c3g4abbg9652g46c360084730": ["T-thanks!  And 'pologies. And... erm... bye!", "b2c582af-bc69-48b3-a004-648562dab404", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "53465c59-37b0-58b0-d7af-145dcefa0888"], "ha190435bg443ag406eg8632g45409913b3f9": ["Oh, <i>wonderful</i> job.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "4f304960-f2b4-62df-bb61-71e1645464e9"], "hc063ba75gfafbg4d8bgb649ge101cefeefe8": ["A word of warning, <i>chief</i>. Don't stand between me and my vengeance.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "6391e370-d1a0-663b-c8b0-a400f1461651"], "h11cb28b5g42ebg4890g9513g995f9ee7b7d9": ["Mizora - the prisoner at your camp. <i>Where was she taken?</i>", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "6771e9d8-8c42-f567-1504-59ddb6efa93c"], "h2f4b5c3ag009fg4273ga0fege01c03cea3be": ["Spike - the bruiser. <i>Where is he?</i>", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "3422a785-b3c0-b067-086c-36804e4fee6f"], "h8a48b6c3g7bc7g4eafg8e4fga85028e0b9de": ["The c-camp. East-ways. Spike's prob'ly gettin' his jollies in the torture-cell.", "b2c582af-bc69-48b3-a004-648562dab404", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "cccaa95a-d747-6c34-f8ca-4ea90e416a65"], "hec0555f8g4e15g4fcdg8a9dg868d8b7f7efe": ["Don't think so. I'll take the lead.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "a53e389d-82be-1758-7585-54a473cb5f08"], "h3fa81740gcd59g4b82g8215g20690743170f": ["<i>Damn you.</i>", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "1def48d6-9edc-42cd-8413-22fd2bbe7fad"], "h11b7b3ccgb563g40e3g8144ge7183fb88847": ["I'll take that gold back. Now.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "4d3e98ed-b0ce-40c2-ec48-a216370e2599"], "h2b34c341gd3b7g45f3gaecagab80b661db79": ["A-all right, fine. Take it - take... wait. It's... it's gone!", "b2c582af-bc69-48b3-a004-648562dab404", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "ee99fdc6-bcf8-ddf0-57de-4642b90234fd"], "h368070a6gf12eg44a2gac67g3b52db617c3e": ["A-all right, fine. Take it - take it all! Now... can I go...?", "b2c582af-bc69-48b3-a004-648562dab404", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "fd8e7ffa-df73-85ce-c45f-902f88f675f8"], "he3483717g2341g4a62g8ac3g9e409f357cc3": ["Tell me <i>everything</i> you know.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "545e7a72-ec5f-56cf-d350-dd52f261b5ea"], "h612e202eg0641g49b7gafb4g660b84505d22": ["T-there's a goblin camp nearby - I can get you inside, no hassle! You can loot it, do whatever you like!", "b2c582af-bc69-48b3-a004-648562dab404", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "c09c4bfd-caa4-f9ee-1641-cd4abd0415a4"], "h566f7326g0acdg4116gbcc1gb93201797ab8": ["There's a hidden path, p-past the bridge into the camp. Over the side before you reach the first guards. Easy.", "b2c582af-bc69-48b3-a004-648562dab404", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "32092c91-fc9d-bb03-f52e-5f5d9ac9432d"], "h708f94b4g196eg4df6g90c2gcb867ec82c9b": ["I'm feeling merciful. Get out of here, goblin.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "a72ba131-2090-3d23-71c1-a328f389848e"], "h2617549ag5fb1g4901g8e4fg7e0d96b65e69": ["T-thanks!  And 'pologies. And... erm... bye!", "b2c582af-bc69-48b3-a004-648562dab404", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "e8c5f962-e981-0ed5-e78c-3f5ec635e09a"], "hd48f4ec7g3584g4272ga14egad26e94280c4": ["<i>Chk. </i>I'd have slit his throat and drank the drippings.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "664c8f68-feae-279d-36bb-3a09b454ac48"], "h10d82710g7fe6g4352g9216g76b681496101": ["Oh, <i>wonderful</i> job.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "b3844cfe-9f1e-a69d-4448-5aa193acdf79"], "h9b4a880eg2c77g4b78gae97gddaa2eb6279f": ["A word of warning, <i>chief</i>. Don't stand between me and my vengeance.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "059690bc-1a4f-f5ad-76fa-b4fc10832daf"], "h0868f315ga9e5g47dcg805dg9269464f78f5": ["<i>Deliver the final blow.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "52ce1756-03d3-e4e2-32ec-18e4317ebd87"], "hca5d961dg0123g4fcfgb14bgeeb902e7cf80": ["N-n-noo!", "b2c582af-bc69-48b3-a004-648562dab404", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "cb14df8f-1446-21e2-6ba2-48eef7a5fade"], "he5827d11g8449g4a8fg9318g3765d45ad25c": ["P-please. I'll tell you what you want to know, captain-Blade-sir!", "b2c582af-bc69-48b3-a004-648562dab404", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "3a01ac8b-554f-0e53-f622-ee0a9d9d562d"], "h7dafbbd0gaed5g40degaa8cgf41a5fe75cbc": ["Wake up, dammit. It's time I had answers.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "506f4139-4e13-25f2-e644-1aec40ccda79"]}